{"tid":634011,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"戴綠帽係咩感受？","createTime":"2018-04-18T22:49:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T04:10:15.000Z","uid":74454,"like":34,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"acb62df318ee48b4da21af3356e212f16d5dd7a8","tid":634011,"uid":74454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T22:49:53.000Z","msg":"我知道係乜撚野感受了<br />\n分左手一個月先俾我發現由聖誕戴到而家<br />\n原來種感覺係咁撚難受<br />\n自問由細到大都係諗得好理想<br />\n係想同女朋友一生一世嘅嗰種人<br />\n一心一意對女朋友好好 當正主人咁看待<br />\n但係而家 不了 <br />\n個世界點對我 我一定會報復<br />\n我要屌撚盡晒天下女 等你地咁鍾意西隧通車呀拿<br />\n有食錯冇放過 屌撚死晒你地班死八婆<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">仆街死啦食屎狗港女</span></span>"},{"pid":"bcbb328c661c2adbf0853e13943886b389068085","tid":634011,"uid":73241,"like":18,"dislike":5,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T22:52:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/19/065200_b761ec179587e9345cabe4148976d39b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F19%2F065200_b761ec179587e9345cabe4148976d39b.png&h=cef9ee57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09a10da3cb4ad5fff72f7e26b7d16003a729ef9e","tid":634011,"uid":74454,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcbb328c661c2adbf0853e13943886b389068085","tid":634011,"uid":73241,"like":18,"dislike":5,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T22:52:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/19/065200_b761ec179587e9345cabe4148976d39b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F19%2F065200_b761ec179587e9345cabe4148976d39b.png&h=cef9ee57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T22:56:57.000Z","msg":"全部港女都係雞係公廁 唔屌對自己唔撚住<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">女人含我撚死</span></span>